code: import axios from'axios';var baseUrl='/api/patients';var getAll=function getAll(){return axios.get(baseUrl).then(function(response){return response.data;});};var getOne=function getOne(id){return axios.get("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id)).then(function(response){return response.data;});};var create=function create(newObject){return axios.post(baseUrl,newObject).then(function(response){return response.data;});};var update=function update(id,newObject){return axios.put("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id),newObject).then(function(response){return response.data;});};var deleteOne=function deleteOne(id){return axios.delete("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id)).then(function(response){return response.data;});};export default{getAll:getAll,getOne:getOne,create:create,update:update,deleteOne:deleteOne};
